name: A Creators Tale - Fear Release
description:
There will be only one creation of this piece. If it is now yours, Congratulations. There is only one commitment required and that is that you pass it on once this particular journey or obstacle has been overcome for you.
Sometimes you create feeling unworthy.
You may create with a feeling of being inferior. Let this be a message of reprogramming. A message to remind you that the language of which you use to speak to yourself, is a language that only you understand. Say something different. No more self deprivation. No more lack for if you feel there is none to lose, there truly is everything to gain. 
Hold these words in your mind, heart and daily thoughts.
